                    <h4>Age Group</h4>
            <ul>
                        <li><a href="/web/20180713090755/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_Age_of_Target_Population=Adult%20%2819%20to%2044%20years%29&amp;fLockTerm=Adult%2B%2819%2Bto%2B44%2Byears%29">Adult (19 to 44 years)</a></li>                      
                        <li><a href="/web/20180713090755/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_Age_of_Target_Population=Aged%20%2865%20to%2079%20years%29&amp;fLockTerm=Aged%2B%2865%2Bto%2B79%2Byears%29">Aged (65 to 79 years)</a></li>                      
                        <li><a href="/web/20180713090755/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_Age_of_Target_Population=Aged%2C%2080%20and%20over&amp;fLockTerm=Aged%252c%2B80%2Band%2Bover">Aged, 80 and over</a></li>                      
                        <li><a href="/web/20180713090755/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_Age_of_Target_Population=Middle%20Age%20%2845%20to%2064%20years%29&amp;fLockTerm=Middle%2BAge%2B%2845%2Bto%2B64%2Byears%29">Middle Age (45 to 64 years)</a></li>                      
            </ul>
                    <h4>UMLS Concepts <a href="/web/20180713090755/https://www.guideline.gov/help-and-about/search-browse/umls-concepts" class="what-is">(what is this?)</a></h4>
                <div class="field">
                    <h5 class="field-label">ICD9CM</h5>
                    <div class="field-content">
<a href="/web/20180713090755/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0302378&amp;fLockTerm=Chronic+airway+obstruction%2c+not+elsewhere+classified">Chronic airway obstruction, not elsewhere classified</a>
 (496), <a href="/web/20180713090755/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0009088&amp;fLockTerm=Cluster+headache+syndrome%2c+unspecified">Cluster headache syndrome, unspecified</a>
 (339.00), <a href="/web/20180713090755/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0009088&amp;fLockTerm=Cluster+headache+syndrome%2c+unspecified">Cluster headache syndrome, unspecified</a>
 (339.02), <a href="/web/20180713090755/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0018802&amp;fLockTerm=Congestive+heart+failure%2c+unspecified">Congestive heart failure, unspecified</a>
 (428.0), <a href="/web/20180713090755/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0010676&amp;fLockTerm=Cystic+fibrosis+without+mention+of+meconium+ileus">Cystic fibrosis without mention of meconium ileus</a>
 (277.00), <a href="/web/20180713090755/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0018799&amp;fLockTerm=Heart+disease%2c+unspecified">Heart disease, unspecified</a>
 (429.9), <a href="/web/20180713090755/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0018801&amp;fLockTerm=Heart+failure%2c+unspecified">Heart failure, unspecified</a>
 (428.9), <a href="/web/20180713090755/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0155917&amp;fLockTerm=Lung+involvement+in+other+diseases+classified+elsewhere">Lung involvement in other diseases classified elsewhere</a>
